channel.title: In-fexis Released[Most Professional PI]
channel.description:
[center][img]http://i.imgur.com/GoWV0.png[/img][/center] [s]Firstly I'd like to ask the moderators and administrators why In-fexis always ends up to MoparScape. Secondly, all releases here that's been released and people faking my name is false. I'm the real MoparScape, for proof feel free to private message me on the other RSPS community websites.[/s] Proof I'm the actual Infexis https://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php?topic=531557.msg3884034#msg3884034 and https://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,531557.msg3884442.html#msg3884442
[IMG]http://i51.tinypic.com/2mgqek7.jpg[/img] I decided to release Infexis because I have not been working on anything for a long time now. Infexis.. with that I mean to make a old days feeling of RuneScape. What else it has is lots of details, with details I mean things such as.. be able to milk cows too have most npc spawns, that's just two examples of many. There's also some quests, in my opinion quests are important and good for the community.. here are some quests that are done. The reason why I am releasing this is because I've moved onto Shard Revolution. By the way, this is a Project Insanity. [ul][li]Cook's Assistant[/li] [li]Dragon Slayer[/li] [li]Desert Treasure[/li] [li]Horror from the Deep[/li] [li]Recipe for Disaster[/li] [li]Imp Catcher - [URL=http://"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZyY02fCwOtc"]Video[/URL][/li][/ul] Here are some more current features. [ul][li]Deposit Box[/li] [li]Skill Interface[/li] [li]99 Level Interface[/li] [li]Ship Traveling[/li] [li]Genie Lamp/Event[/li][/ul] And here's some other features. [ul][li]Over 3200 NPC Spawns[/li] [li]50+ Shops[/li] [li]Most NPC Drops[/li][/ul] Okay, I've listed the most important features. More media will come soon. Please keep the useless spamming & flaming out of this thread.. [size=12pt]Infexis Media[/size] [IMG]http://i55.tinypic.com/20idmr6.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i56.tinypic.com/9zlngn.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i55.tinypic.com/30how3n.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i51.tinypic.com/s67q81.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i55.tinypic.com/vqodo5.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i53.tinypic.com/2ymymmw.jpg[/img] [size=12pt]Download Links[/size] [url=http://up.ht/yp9wNt]UppIT - Download Infexis_Source.zip[/url] A '[B]rep[/B]' would be appreicated if you do like the source or going to use.
Please comment and share your thoughts.
